categories: Category:Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II actors

nodes.text: Dylan Haggerty is an actor whose Star Wars work includes the video game Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II, where he played a bounty hunter in the game's live action cutscenes, credited as "Bounty Hunter 2." Haggerty has also appeared in films such as Con-Air and in television series such as The X-Files and 24.
